Package ec.proctexture

Class SaveImagesStatistics

java.lang.Object
ec.Statistics
ec.proctexture.SaveImagesStatistics
All Implemented Interfaces:
Setup, Singleton, Serializable
public class SaveImagesStatistics extends Statistics
Saves all images at termination, and optionally every N generations. Also saves a higher resolution rendering of the best image.

23.1.0
